BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cadillac Crew
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261023T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261023T213000
DTSTAMP:20260707T064157Z
UID:occ-468@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Tori Sampson's drama: four activists in a Virginia civil right
 s office ask whether the movement's equality includes women.\n\nTori Samps
 on's play unfolds in a Virginia civil rights office on the day of a much-a
 nticipated Rosa Parks speech\, where four activists start asking whether t
 he movement's promise of equality extends to women. It reclaims the storie
 s of the overlooked organizers behind desegregation\, with more humor than
  the setup suggests. Karlotta Washington directs for the Conyers Rockdale 
 Council for the Arts. Runs through October 25.
GEO:33.6671075;-84.0180229
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T063344Z
LOCATION:Conyers Rockdale Council for the Arts\, 910 Center St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://conyersarts.org/calender-of-events/cadillac-crew/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Vanya and Sonia and Masha and Spike
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261023T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261023T213000
DTSTAMP:20260707T064157Z
UID:occ-1260@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Christopher Durang's Chekhov-riffing comedy: a movie-star sist
 er\, her young boyfriend\, and a family farmhouse up for sale.\n\nChristop
 her Durang's comedy borrows its names and its moods from Chekhov\, then le
 ts them loose in present-day Pennsylvania. Siblings Vanya and Sonia have s
 pent their quiet lives in the family farmhouse\; their movie-star sister M
 asha blows in for the weekend with her much younger boyfriend Spike and an
 nounces she's selling the place. Rivalry\, regret\, and a costume party fo
 llow. The play won the 2013 Tony Award for Best Play\; this production com
 es from Arcadia Theater.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T063344Z
LOCATION:Arcadia Theater\, 180 Academy St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/vanya-sasha-masha-spike-tickets-279857
END:VEVENT
