DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261213T171500
DTSTAMP:20260707T064157Z
UID:occ-1445@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:A play from Pumphouse Players\, staged in their 70-seat conver
 ted 1940s cinema.\n\nA play from Pumphouse Players\, one of Georgia's olde
 st continuously operating community theatre companies. The company perform
 s in a converted 1940s cinema with just 70 seats\, so no one watches from 
 a distance.
