BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:12 Angry Jurors
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270128T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270128T223000
DTSTAMP:20260707T064157Z
UID:occ-836@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Reginald Rose's jury-room drama: eleven guilty votes\, one hol
 dout\, and a murder verdict hinging on reasonable doubt.\n\nReginald Rose'
 s classic deliberation drama\, here in the retitled version that opens the
  jury room to a cast of any gender. A teenager stands accused of murdering
  his father\, and the first vote comes back eleven to one for guilty. The 
 lone holdout wants to talk it through\, and one hot afternoon in one room\
 , the case starts to come apart. From Southside Theatre Guild\, an all-vol
 unteer community theatre running since 1973.
GEO:33.5672762;-84.5821546
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T063344Z
LOCATION:Southside Theatre Guild\, 20 W Campbellton St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://tockify.com/stgevents/detail/1026/1801184400000
END:VEVENT
