 phouse Players\, one of Georgia's oldest continuously operating community 
 theatre companies. Their home is a converted 1940s cinema with just 70 sea
 ts\, so no one sits far from the action.
GEO:34.1644344;-84.7971239
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T063344Z
LOCATION:Pumphouse Players\, 114 W Main St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
